description: This indicator shows the annual growth rate of maritime freight transport betweeen EU and non-EU countries, based on gross weight of goods (expressed in tonnes) handled in main EU ports. The indicator is calculated for total goods handled, goods loaded and goods unloaded in ports.
title: Growth of maritime transport
